{"tid":1261322,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果 A 系列處理器效能會更猛，因為 Arm CPU 首席架構師跳槽到蘋果了","createTime":"2019-06-27T07:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T09:17:32.000Z","uid":221827,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea2f05834c99c02c8932be6703f17b4dcf30177","tid":1261322,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"曾經參與打造Arm Cortex A57、A72、A76 CPU設計的首席架構師Mike Filippo，稍早在其個人Linkedin更新資料顯示已經加盟蘋果，意味接下來蘋果在A系列處理器效能表現將可能進一步提昇。<br />\n<br />\n相比市場主流行動處理器效能表現，蘋果打造的A系列處理器始終成為業界比較對象，因此原本在Arm擔任首席架構師、擁有Cortex A57、A72、A76 CPU設計經驗，同時也分別擔任Arm代號Hercules、Ares (即後來推出的Neoverse N1)，以及接下來即將推出的Zeus平台設計推手，顯然Mike Filippo加盟蘋果將引起不少關注。<br />\n<br />\n除了曾經在Arm負責CPU架構設計，Mike Filippo過去也曾先後在AMD、Intel擔任CPU及平台架構師。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果從iPhone 4開始導入首款自行設計的A4處理器，並且在去年推出的iPhone XS系列、iPhone XR採用A12 Bionic處理器，期間除了標榜成為業界第一個以64位元架構打造手機使用處理器的廠商，在當時推出的A7處理器強調效能可達PlayStation 3、Xbox 360等級，同時也在A9處理器開始加入協同處理器設計，更在A11 Fusion處理器開始加入名為Neural Engine的神經網路專用加速電路模組，藉此提昇人工智慧運算效率。<br />\n<br />\n而架構方面，蘋果A系列處理器不僅在64位元架構達成軟硬體整合效果，更善用Arm big.LITTLE，以及HMP (heterogeneous multi-processing,異質多程運算)模式加快處理器執行效率，同時也開始加入蘋果自有設計的GPU，使處理器整體運算效能設計不再受限先前Imagination Technologies旗下PowerVR GPU，可以有更高運算效能調度彈性。<br />\n<br />\n不過，從目前Mike Filippo才加入蘋果陣營，顯然對於今年即將應用在新款iPhone的A13處理器並不會有太大助力，預期蘋果明年推出的新款A系列處理器才會有更明顯不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/tw/mobile/img/2019-06/27/5360417/hat7029_1_5aae980c4957a3c8627a58da6fdadeed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Ftw%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-06%2F27%2F5360417%2Fhat7029_1_5aae980c4957a3c8627a58da6fdadeed.jpg&h=0d0686f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/213406/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F213406%2F1%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=c73ebd21\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/213406/1/</a>"},{"pid":"311a37456951a5df6647966688703905bae0e45a","tid":1261322,"uid":255744,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"arm都就快轉架構，棄將過檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fc434579da83869784b64f3e260b6fbdd37751","tid":1261322,"uid":109923,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"如果蘋果當年無賣到arm股份，依家應該壟斷緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1c187b8658ac554462adcdb5b6f1c7c78d5e6a","tid":1261322,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311a37456951a5df6647966688703905bae0e45a","tid":1261322,"uid":255744,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"arm都就快轉架構，棄將過檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"而家trend係直頭唔用arm，因為唔想俾專利費"},{"pid":"dc6dc5d1812bad1b69fc4ab6cfe605ab041d8247","tid":1261322,"uid":158301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311a37456951a5df6647966688703905bae0e45a","tid":1261322,"uid":255744,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"arm都就快轉架構，棄將過檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"arm 轉架構？<br />\n有無多 d 資料？"},{"pid":"f74889b3ba10df98f6ecc1c7bf9326cda4c45566","tid":1261322,"uid":158301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1c187b8658ac554462adcdb5b6f1c7c78d5e6a","tid":1261322,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311a37456951a5df6647966688703905bae0e45a","tid":1261322,"uid":255744,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"arm都就快轉架構，棄將過檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"而家trend係直頭唔用arm，因為唔想俾專利費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:56:03.00